<p>
  Currently, we support AOL Instant Messenger, Jabber, and <a
  href="/prefs/twitter">Twitter</a>, but we hope to catch up soon for the
  Yahoo, MSN, and yes, IRC addicts out there.
</p>

<ol>
  <li>First, click the "Give me a password!" button below, and we'll give you a secret IM password.</li>
  <li>If you're on AOL Instant Messenger, add <strong>HM Tasks</strong> to your buddy list.</li>
  <li>If you're on Jabber or Google Talk, add <strong>HMTasks@hiveminder.com</strong> to your roster.</li>
  <li>Then, send the IM password to <strong>HM Tasks</strong> like a regular
  IM (but with correct spelling), so we know that you're you.</li>
  <li>Now your todo list is only an IM away.</li>
</ol>

